{
  "page": "House Vypren",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Vypren</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Vypren.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Vypren.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/250px-House_Vypren.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/375px-House_Vypren.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/House_Vypren.svg/500px-House_Vypren.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Coat of arms</th><td>\nA black toad on white lily pad, on green<br />(<i>Vert, a toad sable atop a lilypad argent</i>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Head</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Lucias_Vypren\" title=\"Lucias Vypren\">Lucias Vypren</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">Riverlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Heir</th><td>\nSer <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Vypren\" title=\"Damon Vypren\">Damon Vypren</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Overlords</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tully\" title=\"House Tully\">House Tully</a> (AGOT)</li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baelish\" title=\"House Baelish\">House Baelish</a> (ADWD)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Founded</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">Coming of the Andals</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Vypren</b> is a noble house of the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>. Neither their arms nor their motto has appeared in the books. According to semi-canon sources, they blazon their arms with a black <a href=\"/index.php/Frog\" title=\"Frog\">toad</a> on white lily pad, on green.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#House_Vypren_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Vypren at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Historical_Vyprens\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Historical Vyprens</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Vypren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Coming_of_the_Andals\" title=\"Coming of the Andals\">coming of the Andals</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> warlord <a href=\"/index.php/Vorian_Vypren\" title=\"Vorian Vypren\">Vorian Vypren</a> and his knights were held at bay at the <a href=\"/index.php/Widow%27s_Ford\" title=\"Widow&#39;s Ford\">Widow's Ford</a> for a day and a night by three sons of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darry\" title=\"House Darry\">Darry</a> before finally slaying the Darrys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord Vypren supported <a href=\"/index.php/Harwyn_Hoare\" title=\"Harwyn Hoare\">Harwyn Hardhand</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">King of the Iron Islands</a>, when he warred against the <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Arrec_Durrandon\" title=\"Arrec Durrandon\">Arrec Durrandon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Sabitha_Frey\" title=\"Sabitha Frey\">Sabitha Vypren</a> was married to the gallant Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Forrest_Frey\" title=\"Forrest Frey\">Forrest Frey</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands:_house_tully.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and had at least one son with him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Her father and brothers led the Vyprens in supporting the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a> against the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>, as did the widowed Sabitha herself with <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_rhaenyra_overthrown.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Vypren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Vypren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lucias_Vypren\" title=\"Lucias Vypren\">Lucias Vypren</a> is married to <a href=\"/index.php/Lythene_Frey\" title=\"Lythene Frey\">Lythene Frey</a>, the daughter of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a> and his third wife, <a href=\"/index.php/Amarei_Crakehall\" title=\"Amarei Crakehall\">Amarei Crakehall</a>. Lucias and his son, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Vypren\" title=\"Damon Vypren\">Damon</a>, attend the wedding at the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a> of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Roslin_Frey\" title=\"Roslin Frey\">Roslin Frey</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> which becomes the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Red Wedding</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Vypren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lucias tracks a <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">band of outlaws</a> who may have been part of the group that hanged <a href=\"/index.php/Merrett_Frey\" title=\"Merrett Frey\">Merrett Frey</a> all the way to <a href=\"/index.php/Fairmarket\" title=\"Fairmarket\">Fairmarket</a> before losing them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Vypren_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Vypren at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Vypren&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Vypren at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Vyprens during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lucias_Vypren\" title=\"Lucias Vypren\">Lucias Vypren</a>, the head of the house.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lythene_Frey\" title=\"Lythene Frey\">Lythene Frey</a>, his wife.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Elyana_Vypren\" title=\"Elyana Vypren\">Elyana Vypren</a>, his eldest child. Married to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Wylde\" title=\"Jon Wylde\">Jon Wylde</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Vypren\" title=\"Damon Vypren\">Damon Vypren</a>, his son and heir.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lucias_Vypren\" title=\"Lucias Vypren\">Lucias</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lythene_Frey\" title=\"Lythene Frey\">Lythene<br />Frey</a></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font